1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,060
Here's your man, Nick Skryer.

2
00:00:02,440 --> 00:00:04,680
Facial reconstruction and a memory wipe.

3
00:00:05,400 --> 00:00:09,700
Intelligence has the movement attack in
the refinery in about 90 hours from now.

4
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:11,380
We're ready when he is.

5
00:00:11,700 --> 00:00:14,133
This memory wipe will give
us plenty of time to drop

6
00:00:14,134 --> 00:00:16,580
him in and get him past
the movement's psyprobes.

7
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:19,520
Mindgate's specialty is psyops.

8
00:00:20,340 --> 00:00:22,560
I've done some homework on Mindgate.

9
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:26,420
Your boy's got quite a reputation and it's
not all good.

10
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,340
Okay, he's no boy scout, but Nick Skryer
is Mindgate's best.

11
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:35,266
They dismissed General
Krager, but Skryer stayed with

12
00:00:35,267 --> 00:00:38,460
Mindgate and took his
psychic powers to a new level.

13
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:39,600
The very white man.

14
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:40,700
Oh!

